description:
TAKE YOUR LASHES TO NEW SKY-RISE HEIGHTS!

Create the perfect curl in seconds with the MCoBeauty COMB EYELASH CURLER. This luxe lash-curling device ensures intensely lifted lashes every time, without any breakages or damage, thanks to the gentle silicone padding, while the lash-separating comb guides individual lash hairs into the ultimate feathery curl.

QUICK FACTS:

  • DELIVERS RESULTS JUST LIKE A LASH LIFT
  • COMB SEPARATES AND LENGTHENS WITHOUT CRIMPING
  • REPLACEMENT SILICONE PAD INCLUDED

DIRECTIONS:

Ensure lashes are clean and dry. Open the eyelash curler and look downwards. Carefully insert your lashes into the curler, then gently squeeze closed and hold for 5-10 seconds. Release and repeat on the other eye.
name: Mcobeauty Comb Eyelash Curler Each
